Javascript is a wonderful language composed of objects, functions and landmines.

Javascript is for more than dancing unicorns and rainbows. The days of fighting browser bugs and stepping on language landmines are almost gone. With ECMAScript 5 ("use strict";), JSLint and simplifying your language features:

Javascript is cool! <Dr Who in a Stetson>


